## 📌 Overview

This project focuses on analyzing and forecasting Walmart’s weekly sales using **Time Series techniques (ARIMA & SARIMA)**.
It helps in understanding **sales trends, seasonality**, and predicting future demand to support **inventory planning**.

---

## 📂 Dataset

The dataset contains **6,000+ records** with the following features:

* 🏬 Store ID
* 📅 Date
* 💰 Weekly Sales
* 🌡 Temperature
* ⛽ Fuel Price
* 📊 CPI (Consumer Price Index)
* 📉 Unemployment Rate

---

## ⚙️ Workflow

1. 📥 Data Loading & Preprocessing
2. 🔍 Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
3. 📆 Time Series Transformation
4. 📊 Seasonal Decomposition (Trend, Seasonality, Residual)
5. 🤖 Model Building using **ARIMA & SARIMA**
6. 📈 Forecasting Future Sales (12 Weeks)
7. 📏 Model Evaluation (MSE, RMSE)

